title: Ice Cube Tray with Lid 3 Packs 45 Cubes Large Flexible Silicone Ice Cube Tray BPA Free & Easy Release Ice Cube Moulds for Freezer, for Whisky, Cocktails, Drinks,Baby Food, Freezer
features: Food-Grade Silicone Material: The ice cube tray is made of high-quality food-grade silicone, BPA-free and odorless. Please feel free to use the ice tray to make baby food or other delicious snacks for your family

Silicone Ice Cube Tray with Removable Lid: 100% sealed to avoid diluting food flavor and contaminating the refrigerator. The ice cube moulds will increase in volume during the freezing process. The removable silicone lid design ensures that the ice cubes will not leak out

Easy to Release: 3 high-quality silicone ice cube trays, each ice tray can hold 15 large cubes. The flexible silicone material at the bottom of the tray is easier to demold and convenient to take out ice. Just press the bottom to take out the ice cubes.

Multifunctional Ice Cube Tray: Applicable to -94℉ ~ 140℉/-70℃ ~ 60℃, not easy to crack and break under long-term freezing, very suitable for cooling cocktails, whiskey, tequila, vodka or other less diluted drinks, and can also be DIY with fruits, ice cream and other foods according to your favorite flavors.
Easy to Clean and Store: The ice cube tray can be stacked to save you space, and can be put in the dishwasher for cleaning after use, freeing your hands.
Note: The volume will increase after the liquid solidifies. Do not add too much water to prevent the ice cubes from sticking together and making it easier to get out of the ice cubes.
